тЬЕ [OT HTML Transcripts] Local HTML transcript archive, renderer, and public host for Open Ticket.
тЬЕ [OT Restrictions] Restrict which roles can open a specific ticket option.
тЬЕ [OT Reviews] Review system for Open Ticket! It is very customisable and has lots of features.
тЬЕ [OT SQLite Database] With this plugin, the database will be an SQLite file! It's a must-have for large servers!
тЬЕ [OT Tags] Use tags to quickly reply with a pre-existing text!
тЬЕ [OT Template System] Predefined template system for sending quick messages.
тЬЕ [OT Ticket Forms] An advanced forms plugin for Open Ticket.
тЬЕ [OT Volume Warning] Alerts ticket creators when too many tickets are open, indicating possible response delays.
